B.VM=s(["Stage eggs, oil or butter, spatulas, and pans before the rush starts.","Preheat the flat top fully before cooking.","Cook in controlled batches and pull the eggs before they overcook.","Keep communicating with the runner and the cook when food is getting low."],t.s)
